{"tid":259402,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"想同咁多位dse雞講 如非必要真係唔好返暑期工住","createTime":"2017-05-27T01:18:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-27T05:31:43.000Z","uid":53663,"like":6,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a50cbebcc10bc28cb617469d7ba86b0fd092f374","tid":259402,"uid":53663,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T01:18:52.000Z","msg":"是咁的 小弟家境清貧 趁住呢個假期想搵錢遲啲交學費 <br />\n經一個朋友介紹 入左去一間裝修公司做工人 諗住搵快錢 同埋自己應該應付到ge<br />\n點知第一日返工 上料都上到我虛脫咁濟  做我慢少少又俾啲cfu屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然上完料 我無乜特別野要做 都係做啲輔助cfu嘅野 但係我想講個度超超超大塵 見個個cfu都自備毛巾 我又蠢撚到第一日返工 唔記得帶 搞到一路做 一路吸勁撚多塵 依加諗返起個畫面真係室內沙塵暴咁款<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n放工返到屋企 攰撚到我差啲飯都無力食 夜晚啲肌肉又痛撚到仆街 典下典下咁完全瞓唔著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 碌左幾粒鐘 第二朝又7點起身開工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 自問平時都有打開波 雖然唔大隻 但都唔算孱<br />\n<br />\n其實我想講 如果各位有家境嘅學生哥學生妹 唔好俾同輩或社會影響左 一完中學就急急腳搵工 其實係好蠢架 明明辛苦完自己咁多年 埋頭苦幹學習左咁多年 咁難得有個悠長嘅假期 就應該盡情享受 話知你日日匿埋係屋企打機定打j 總之做自己鐘意嘅野就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有仲有 第時你讀完大專後 返工返到你唔想返都仲要返呀 何必咁做就開始折磨自己 踏入社會呢個地獄呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以上講嘅情況只係for家境有能力嘅學生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不過窮撚們如果可以嘅話 都好好享受下呢個悠長嘅假期啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n講到呢度 我又要去返工了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利伸借朋友ac開post 有感而發"},{"pid":"04d73bc77206a9d40d5036825dfd60f28609c371","tid":259402,"uid":29120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T01:20:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f3031cddeba453a60353912ce441d078d200bf0a","tid":259402,"uid":59192,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T01:21:13.000Z","msg":"邊個番工唔係咁<br />\n再講 你個份workload大啫"},{"pid":"972ae65ba93a6730c69f4d750d7aee4b6bd924fe","tid":259402,"uid":96007,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T01:21:54.000Z","msg":"on9仔搵埋啲唔岩自己嘅工姐"},{"pid":"c2efe9f094a0bca7edce4adaecf4fba07bb0d830","tid":259402,"uid":67689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T01:26:22.000Z","msg":"休息返一頭半個月好啦 除非你有幫手做家務煮飯洗衫果啲 否則對屋企冇返少少貢獻都過唔到自己良心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b3c60b28e5731c7a11c5536dc40ccf0477be73c","tid":259402,"uid":838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T01:30:48.000Z","msg":"唔辛苦邊得世間財<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n覺得辛苦嘅可以轉工呀，最多咪俾人屌幾句"},{"pid":"2ce51c03dbc6b4f24f6c7571b32f61b00c16a761","tid":259402,"uid":35370,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T01:43:45.000Z","msg":"唔係話鼓吹返工做奴隸<br />\n不過我覺得返工見識下社會都係好事<br />\n到時出嚟正式做嘢冇咁怯<br />\n對其他人嘅睇法都會唔同咗<br />\n例如樓主你依家見到裝修工人同地盤佬<br />\n都唔會睇低人哋一線<br />\n而返其他工例如銀行，就可能會對人戒心高咗<br />\n知道世界真係可以好複雜，人心真係好難理解<br />\n而同人交際都自然會得心應手啲<br />\n唔可以再好似以前咁自我中心<br />\n有咩工適合自己，有咩工唔適合，都會多咗認識<br />\n<br />\n當然，唔等錢洗都可以放假輕鬆下<br />\n但返工都唔係壞事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2eb9e387aa8f7168abb352e965a58853f59a28c5","tid":259402,"uid":117822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T01:48:40.000Z","msg":"番工又想舒服又想人工高，做鴨比較適合你。"},{"pid":"afbc4b2d811849a1cf85b9032303459249716a9f","tid":259402,"uid":14361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T02:19:20.000Z","msg":"翻地盤好過裝修<br />\n我自己上年完左DSE都係翻地盤"},{"pid":"f28481c2639d936c3b8961a0baae2dd64ddbe6f7","tid":259402,"uid":39463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T02:22:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我果時考完會考，返速遞都冇你咁誇張，我仲要平時唔運動<br />\n你係唔係用錯力，拉傷肌肉"},{"pid":"1cc4d55d625325d9cf2a91436fdf15d3ee18bf6e","tid":259402,"uid":21924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T02:46:35.000Z","msg":"根本暑期工就係廉價勞工呃鳩班dse 雞<br />\n<br />\n個個講到唔做就無撚用做蛀米大蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2485de53482cc19095bad3c65cf315c50cc5e64","tid":259402,"uid":21924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T02:49:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>根本暑期工就係廉價勞工呃鳩班dse 雞<br />\n<br />\n個個講到唔做就無撚用做蛀米大蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢個年代屋企有少少錢就係錯就係父幹<br />\n<br />\n個個打份牛工搵幾十蚊就周圍打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  笑撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"211311ccdc35d9ac6a6753a2a3b0f4b7a4af2355","tid":259402,"uid":45055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T02:50:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />個時做左日炒散<br />\n之後就冇返過 專心係屋企讀書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"742538dcdbc0e670cba217d6e4c440722e52f6d1","tid":259402,"uid":29351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T04:22:14.000Z","msg":"有啲輕鬆少少你唔做 怪邊個呀"},{"pid":"b8e35001565b70ee25d14533fc6f90b357c65f25","tid":259402,"uid":118915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T04:32:31.000Z","msg":"咁撚廢 仲講話自己打波 你都係滾返屋企做媽寶啦 搬下野咪當做gym 比人屌咪反省下自己係咪咁慢 少少皮肉之苦就係度嘈"},{"pid":"29647868efc8990931a0224a3e5b8acee7c3ce23","tid":259402,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T04:37:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2652b690071eca3e0cfc305f06e09c963e5fcbc0","tid":259402,"uid":53663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T04:38:04.000Z","msg":"其實我主要想講有能力嘅話dse雞們就應該珍惜下假期盡情享受咁姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我份工都唔係重點 我亦都唔係想怨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />巴打們唔洗咁勞氣 可能我表達方式錯左<br />\n不過樓上有巴打都講得啱ge 做暑期工又真係可以吸取唔少經驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"557eb1a0547ac3211248718027dd0f5447bbf4e0","tid":259402,"uid":76804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T04:38:42.000Z","msg":"睇番咩囉<br />\n有d可以識下人一大班幾好玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8daeee5776a1226b0377a6173b34d91d7ef1292b","tid":259402,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T04:38:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d4cdc6ca27a134c9f3b301762859ab29e618d9d3","tid":259402,"uid":46682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T04:39:00.000Z","msg":"呢家啲90後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9786ea7198c488e906a1e82fe6117e5af5eeb6cd","tid":259402,"uid":36291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T04:44:56.000Z","msg":"係份工辛苦姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52fb09686d2eea4720b30a9ef1235e599f493363","tid":259402,"uid":24641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T05:02:44.000Z","msg":"幾錢日"},{"pid":"57fc8b716e569236d810d29ceee4257f6d74ccc6","tid":259402,"uid":54791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T05:26:55.000Z","msg":"渣ge"},{"pid":"a6cf57a996e1cb946ef602fbc10ccb9ffccef25e","tid":259402,"uid":22095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T05:28:40.000Z","msg":"第一次做 做711 執貨好過啦<br />\n你做咁耐都唔會比到學費個幾萬蚊<br />\n想試下做嘅受下氣嘅<br />\n做輕鬆d 執下貨做收銀 起碼都輕鬆d<br />\n地盤唔係比18 19呢d後生做"},{"pid":"b67134a0fce5e1a1c9371b2237ca1085fbf8d0ae","tid":259402,"uid":26711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T05:31:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>根本暑期工就係廉價勞工呃鳩班dse 雞<br />\n<br />\n個個講到唔做就無撚用做蛀米大蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  果陣dse後hea足半年 而家岩岩grad 一個月已經差唔多搵到果半年既錢<br />\n不如拎果半年做自己鍾意既野 grad左就無機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}